			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Better way to do this:
<br />

<br />
1) Use a Levitation item, stay up near top of water, max range from mob to break a spawn. Range does affect aggro. Less they changed it long as you are far, light blues will not add.
<br />

<br />
2) Use a BOLT spell, your most powerful, to pull, when you get Lava Bolt this becomes a cinch because the mob is half dead right off with one hit. Fire twice if need. Trick is to kill first mob uber fast, just blast it then let pet smash the second oen slower, which also helps split the spawn. 
<br />
There's variatons on this but root items/SOW help.
<br />
Note fire is rarely resisted by these guys. because of their whimpy hit points/damage output, fire pets can be great if you know what your doing.
<br />

<br />
3) learn the pathing, it's really sick xp because you can, assuming no competition, go in a circle clearing the little buggers, constantly <img src="images/smiles/icon_wink.gif" alt="Wink" border="0" /><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=304331" target="_blank" class="postlink"><span style="font-weight: bold"><span style="color: red">REDORIOUS.....ARCHMAGE.....KARANA</span></span></a>
